00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:10,000
[English subtitles are available]

2
00:01:29,820 --> 00:01:35,050
[Pledge of Allegiance]

3
00:01:35,479 --> 00:01:37,810
[Episode 12]

4
00:02:24,730 --> 00:02:25,320
Thank you.

5
00:02:26,329 --> 00:02:26,770
Wait.

6
00:02:29,810 --> 00:02:30,829
I'll go and eat at home.

7
00:02:30,900 --> 00:02:31,640
Eat here now.

8
00:02:33,770 --> 00:02:35,100
I can't eat now.

9
00:02:35,760 --> 00:02:36,400
Then give it back to me.

10
00:02:40,650 --> 00:02:41,550
You're all the same.

11
00:02:41,780 --> 00:02:42,700
If you can't eat,

12
00:02:42,780 --> 00:02:43,670
put it back in the basket.

13
00:02:44,340 --> 00:02:46,390
My mother asked me to take the eggs home.

14
00:02:49,950 --> 00:02:51,040
How many brothers do you have?

15
00:02:52,140 --> 00:02:52,760
Four.

16
00:02:53,400 --> 00:02:54,210
If you take this home,

17
00:02:54,480 --> 00:02:56,210
your mother will give the eggs to your brothers.

18
00:02:56,680 --> 00:02:57,630
You won't be able to eat anything.

19
00:02:58,940 --> 00:03:00,250
She told you to be sensible

20
00:03:00,810 --> 00:03:02,770
not because you're the elder sister who needs to take care of little brothers,

21
00:03:03,240 --> 00:03:04,570
but because you're a girl.

22
00:03:05,210 --> 00:03:06,160
Either you'll starve to death,

23
00:03:06,470 --> 00:03:08,100
or be sold like an animal.

24
00:03:08,540 --> 00:03:09,180
If you don't fight for yourself,

25
00:03:09,200 --> 00:03:10,090
you won't get anything.

26
00:03:14,030 --> 00:03:14,830
Only when you're full,

27
00:03:14,930 --> 00:03:15,800
you'll have the power to fight.

28
00:03:19,180 --> 00:03:20,180
Eat slowly.

29
00:03:20,280 --> 00:03:21,480
There's more. Don't choke.

30
00:03:35,240 --> 00:03:35,810
Mr. Zhang.

31
00:03:36,700 --> 00:03:37,470
It’s late.

32
00:03:38,010 --> 00:03:39,130
Why are you in the Ji'e Alley?

33
00:03:39,780 --> 00:03:41,060
Since you want to see it,

34
00:03:43,550 --> 00:03:44,880
why don't you do so openly?

35
00:03:45,890 --> 00:03:46,550
Excuse me.

36
00:03:47,329 --> 00:03:48,079
I'm just

37
00:03:49,220 --> 00:03:49,950
a little surprised.

38
00:04:30,830 --> 00:04:31,380
Mr. Zhang,

39
00:04:32,170 --> 00:04:33,700
why did you only give eggs to girls?

40
00:04:36,670 --> 00:04:37,750
Ten years ago,

41
00:04:38,890 --> 00:04:40,190
I got separated from my sister.

42
00:04:42,270 --> 00:04:43,260
I'll never know

43
00:04:44,100 --> 00:04:44,740
whether she is full or hungry

44
00:04:44,760 --> 00:04:46,300
or if she can have an egg.

45
00:04:48,120 --> 00:04:49,260
Every time I think about it,

46
00:04:50,540 --> 00:04:51,760
I feel very sad.

47
00:04:53,000 --> 00:04:54,110
I've been looking for her for ten years.

48
00:04:55,620 --> 00:04:56,210
I couldn't find her.

49
00:04:57,460 --> 00:04:59,190
So I secretly thought

50
00:04:59,890 --> 00:05:02,130
if I could find her by doing things like this.

51
00:05:03,390 --> 00:05:04,340
Maybe there's a chance that when I look up,

52
00:05:04,340 --> 00:05:06,340
the girl who comes for the egg is my sister.

53
00:05:07,640 --> 00:05:08,650
But I was scared.

54
00:05:10,540 --> 00:05:11,450
Ten years have passed.

55
00:05:12,780 --> 00:05:14,010
Can I still recognize her?

56
00:05:16,880 --> 00:05:17,410
Also,

57
00:05:17,940 --> 00:05:19,850
I gave an egg to a boy before.

58
00:05:21,490 --> 00:05:22,970
But he became an Brocade-clad Guard.

59
00:05:25,490 --> 00:05:27,050
Mr Zhang doesn't like the Brocade-clad Guard?

60
00:05:32,680 --> 00:05:33,870
How can I like someone

61
00:05:33,890 --> 00:05:34,740
once killed my relatives

62
00:05:35,690 --> 00:05:36,740
and my whole family,

63
00:05:37,920 --> 00:05:39,760
then put me into the Court Entertainment Bureau.

64
00:05:42,360 --> 00:05:43,320
You must be saved

65
00:05:44,510 --> 00:05:46,400
by the nobleman.

66
00:05:47,210 --> 00:05:48,390
You must think that

67
00:05:48,909 --> 00:05:49,930
he saved me

68
00:05:50,530 --> 00:05:51,480
and make me be his concubine.

69
00:06:00,340 --> 00:06:02,390
When I was young, my father raised me as a boy

70
00:06:03,360 --> 00:06:04,370
and let me learning.

71
00:06:05,410 --> 00:06:06,460
I was ambitious in the court.

72
00:06:06,910 --> 00:06:08,400
But I realized when I grew up,

73
00:06:09,270 --> 00:06:11,380
it's hard for women to be in court.

74
00:06:12,130 --> 00:06:12,860
Don't mention that

75
00:06:14,980 --> 00:06:16,860
I've been in the Court Entertainment Bureau.

76
00:06:20,300 --> 00:06:22,280
I thought my life would never change.

77
00:06:22,850 --> 00:06:24,050
Until I met him.

78
00:06:28,710 --> 00:06:30,000
He gave me a choice

79
00:06:31,290 --> 00:06:33,050
and made me live again.

80
00:06:33,580 --> 00:06:34,860
Lord Lu, do you know the feeling of

81
00:06:34,890 --> 00:06:36,400
being saved

82
00:06:38,010 --> 00:06:39,120
when your heart has already died?

83
00:06:53,620 --> 00:06:54,630
I'm just like you.

84
00:06:56,540 --> 00:06:57,600
I'm the descendant of a sinful official, too.

85
00:06:58,880 --> 00:06:59,600
I'm someone

86
00:07:00,800 --> 00:07:01,990
who is supposed to die.

87
00:07:04,560 --> 00:07:06,340
Maybe God pitied me, too.

88
00:07:07,140 --> 00:07:08,720
He arranged a few noblemen for me.

89
00:07:09,500 --> 00:07:10,180
One

90
00:07:10,830 --> 00:07:11,520
saved me

91
00:07:12,100 --> 00:07:13,090
and raised me.

92
00:07:14,800 --> 00:07:16,480
One was my colleague and my best friend.

93
00:07:17,650 --> 00:07:18,450
And one

94
00:07:23,580 --> 00:07:24,550
who gave me hope

95
00:07:25,550 --> 00:07:26,810
and let me justify for my father's crime.

96
00:07:29,460 --> 00:07:30,950
You shouldn't have told me this.

97
00:07:36,120 --> 00:07:37,460
Then who should I tell?

98
00:07:39,320 --> 00:07:41,020
We just met by chance.

99
00:07:41,890 --> 00:07:43,440
We may never meet again.

100
00:07:44,220 --> 00:07:46,530
We just comfort each other

101
00:07:47,500 --> 00:07:48,480
by telling secrets.

102
00:07:51,400 --> 00:07:52,650
I met Mr. Zhang

103
00:07:53,250 --> 00:07:54,720
because my colleague,  who is also my best friend

104
00:07:55,090 --> 00:07:56,370
went to your store to buy cloth.

105
00:07:57,310 --> 00:07:58,080
It's because of him.

106
00:08:00,340 --> 00:08:01,980
Your friend

107
00:08:02,110 --> 00:08:03,190
had a son.

108
00:08:04,090 --> 00:08:04,450
Yes.

109
00:08:07,490 --> 00:08:08,350
But,

110
00:08:09,480 --> 00:08:10,310
he can’t see his child.

111
00:08:12,240 --> 00:08:13,680
He was killed by rebels

112
00:08:14,250 --> 00:08:15,290
when solving cases in Mount Guanyin.

113
00:08:20,060 --> 00:08:21,820
A rebel

114
00:08:20,620 --> 00:08:22,030
[Xie Kengran]

115
00:08:22,380 --> 00:08:22,880
with a gost-faced mask.

116
00:08:27,800 --> 00:08:29,050
I will kill him

117
00:08:29,810 --> 00:08:30,660
for Xie Kengran,

118
00:08:31,270 --> 00:08:32,220
and

119
00:08:32,809 --> 00:08:34,030
for those innocent people.

120
00:09:22,990 --> 00:09:24,050
I don't believe you.

121
00:09:24,280 --> 00:09:25,620
I just want to get promoted.

122
00:09:26,550 --> 00:09:27,380
You're not that kind of person.

123
00:09:32,740 --> 00:09:33,690
What kind of person am I?

124
00:09:35,000 --> 00:09:36,860
The Li Dongfang, who talk about the world with me

125
00:09:37,010 --> 00:09:37,620
is you.

126
00:09:41,660 --> 00:09:43,110
I don't know what your motive is.

127
00:09:43,720 --> 00:09:44,790
I don't want to know either.

128
00:09:45,900 --> 00:09:47,340
Your selfish motive will definitely affect you.

129
00:09:47,500 --> 00:09:47,950
Therefore,

130
00:09:48,470 --> 00:09:49,630
you must avoid arousing suspicion.

131
00:09:51,270 --> 00:09:52,020
For the sake of the world,

132
00:09:52,660 --> 00:09:54,650
only Lu Zheng can do this.

133
00:09:57,440 --> 00:09:58,420
You talked about

134
00:09:59,000 --> 00:10:00,350
so many great principles.

135
00:10:00,900 --> 00:10:01,810
To put it bluntly,

136
00:10:02,130 --> 00:10:03,920
you just want to find out the old rebel case

137
00:10:04,190 --> 00:10:05,590
of the year of Hong Wu.

138
00:10:06,050 --> 00:10:07,040
Isn't that your selfish motive?

139
00:10:10,060 --> 00:10:11,510
I've never wronged a good man

140
00:10:11,810 --> 00:10:12,930
or let go of a bad guy

141
00:10:12,960 --> 00:10:13,890
because of investigating old cases.

142
00:10:14,510 --> 00:10:15,390
You help the rebels

143
00:10:15,650 --> 00:10:16,730
for the officials.

144
00:10:17,360 --> 00:10:18,590
The arms are transported to Beijing secretly.

145
00:10:18,620 --> 00:10:19,470
Then the war starts.

146
00:10:19,870 --> 00:10:20,610
These lives

147
00:10:20,800 --> 00:10:21,880
will be your fault.

148
00:10:24,460 --> 00:10:25,870
I did something wrong

149
00:10:26,000 --> 00:10:26,970
I was threatened.

150
00:10:27,200 --> 00:10:28,620
I had no choice but to work for the rebels.

151
00:10:28,750 --> 00:10:29,850
This is my selfish motive.

152
00:10:32,770 --> 00:10:33,700
This is a resignation letter.

153
00:10:35,470 --> 00:10:37,010
It's not that the court can't tolerate you.

154
00:10:37,300 --> 00:10:38,950
It's me who can't tolerate you anymore.

155
00:10:40,510 --> 00:10:41,520
You don't deserve

156
00:10:42,390 --> 00:10:43,150
this flying fish clothes.

157
00:10:44,220 --> 00:10:45,630
Leave your uniform and leave.

158
00:10:46,890 --> 00:10:47,840
If you are wanted

159
00:10:48,260 --> 00:10:49,180
or threatened,

160
00:10:49,580 --> 00:10:51,030
you deserve it.

161
00:10:56,470 --> 00:10:57,720
I thought about starting over.

162
00:10:59,350 --> 00:11:00,380
But every time I set out,

163
00:11:00,940 --> 00:11:02,130
I go back to the same start point.

164
00:11:03,030 --> 00:11:04,710
That past is weighing me down forever.

165
00:11:04,740 --> 00:11:05,810
I want to get rid of the past.

166
00:11:07,060 --> 00:11:08,230
I want to be free from guilt.

167
00:11:08,380 --> 00:11:09,310
Don't think about it.

168
00:11:10,300 --> 00:11:11,970
If I see you again, I'll arrest you.

169
00:11:16,020 --> 00:11:17,200
But I thought we were friends.

170
00:11:18,840 --> 00:11:20,180
You said that for a person like you,

171
00:11:20,880 --> 00:11:22,180
nothing ventured,

172
00:11:22,180 --> 00:11:23,210
nothing gained.

173
00:11:23,620 --> 00:11:24,510
No matter how difficult and dangerous the situation is,

174
00:11:27,740 --> 00:11:28,970
you only care about yourself.

175
00:11:29,590 --> 00:11:31,330
You're the one who has no right to talk about the world.

176
00:11:31,690 --> 00:11:32,970
Xie Kengran has every right to keep you away from the dragger.

177
00:11:32,990 --> 00:11:33,640
But you,

178
00:11:35,520 --> 00:11:37,320
you are not the one.

179
00:11:38,300 --> 00:11:39,100
How can you

180
00:11:39,100 --> 00:11:40,320
wear this flying fish clothes?

181
00:11:40,580 --> 00:11:41,620
I was born

182
00:11:41,940 --> 00:11:43,110
not to be friends with people like you.

183
00:11:43,170 --> 00:11:44,690
I despise you from the bottom of my heart.

184
00:12:23,240 --> 00:12:23,810
How is it?

185
00:12:37,710 --> 00:12:38,140
Colonel.

186
00:12:39,260 --> 00:12:39,980
Drink the medicine first.

187
00:12:49,970 --> 00:12:51,190
This is the new draft of the word Za Zi.

188
00:12:51,780 --> 00:12:52,640
Send it to the Fang Gu Hall.

189
00:12:53,380 --> 00:12:53,950
Colone.

190
00:12:54,210 --> 00:12:55,660
Zhang Junqing almost killed you.

191
00:12:56,220 --> 00:12:56,960
Why are you still believe her?

192
00:13:01,440 --> 00:13:03,480
If Zhang Junqing didn't stab me wrong on purpose,

193
00:13:05,260 --> 00:13:06,860
I would have been in hell now.

194
00:13:14,970 --> 00:13:15,950
Since the thirtieth year of Hong Wu,

195
00:13:16,600 --> 00:13:17,530
Song Tianyi

196
00:13:18,340 --> 00:13:19,810
has followed me for battles in Beijing.

197
00:13:25,460 --> 00:13:27,090
His stab

198
00:13:28,520 --> 00:13:30,090
was much more painful

199
00:13:31,420 --> 00:13:32,500
than Zhang Junqing's.

200
00:13:32,970 --> 00:13:36,020
[Zhang’s Silk Store]

201
00:13:45,810 --> 00:13:46,980
After this embroidery,

202
00:13:47,810 --> 00:13:48,740
the moment will come.

203
00:13:52,030 --> 00:13:53,490
Most people embroidery dragon, phoenix

204
00:13:54,270 --> 00:13:54,750
and mandarin ducks.

205
00:13:56,410 --> 00:13:57,640
What are you embroidering?

206
00:14:05,130 --> 00:14:06,810
The sky of Qin city's pavilions are filled with fireworks.

207
00:14:07,470 --> 00:14:09,060
The Han Dynasty's mountains and rivers are embroidered.

208
00:14:10,030 --> 00:14:11,480
I embroidered the landscape of Ming.

209
00:14:15,410 --> 00:14:16,960
When I took over Nanjing,

210
00:14:17,620 --> 00:14:19,280
the last Colonel of Night Scout left with me this.

211
00:14:20,340 --> 00:14:21,290
He is my father.

212
00:14:22,740 --> 00:14:23,830
Actually, my last name was Mu.

213
00:14:25,180 --> 00:14:26,370
I've never heard you mention it.

214
00:14:30,310 --> 00:14:32,550
My father is Mo Jinggao, he was a Night Scout.

215
00:14:33,700 --> 00:14:34,400
When I was young,

216
00:14:35,500 --> 00:14:37,580
I thought he was working for the Eastern Palace.

217
00:14:39,210 --> 00:14:39,860
To be honest,

218
00:14:40,940 --> 00:14:42,050
I still don't know

219
00:14:42,050 --> 00:14:43,230
who he followed.

220
00:14:44,900 --> 00:14:45,570
Hong Wunian.

221
00:14:46,450 --> 00:14:47,770
Li Yan, the Assistant Minister of the Ministry of War.

222
00:14:47,800 --> 00:14:50,000
He used to be a messenger between my father and the Eastern Palace.

223
00:14:51,340 --> 00:14:53,280
Later, Li Yan was arrested by the Imperial Guards

224
00:14:54,050 --> 00:14:55,190
and confessed my father.

225
00:14:56,580 --> 00:14:58,560
My sister and I were imprisoned.

226
00:14:59,060 --> 00:15:00,470
I was sent to the Court Entertainment Bureau.

227
00:15:00,920 --> 00:15:03,290
Fortunately, I was saved by a scholar

228
00:15:04,740 --> 00:15:06,200
and escaped from the Court Entertainment Bureau.

229
00:15:08,050 --> 00:15:09,030
That scholar

230
00:15:09,420 --> 00:15:12,010
is the Grand Secretariat of Wenhua Hall, Yuan Zhongdao.

231
00:15:13,140 --> 00:15:15,090
Lord Yuan arranged me in a secret room.

232
00:15:15,620 --> 00:15:16,990
He advised me to change my name

233
00:15:17,260 --> 00:15:18,480
and live a normal life.

234
00:15:20,680 --> 00:15:22,630
But I insisted on staying with him.

235
00:15:24,580 --> 00:15:26,140
First, I wanted to repay him.

236
00:15:27,270 --> 00:15:28,310
But there was another reason.

237
00:15:29,930 --> 00:15:32,050
The Grand Secretariat of Wenhua Hall

238
00:15:32,860 --> 00:15:34,870
has all the information and spies

239
00:15:34,890 --> 00:15:36,560
of the 13 Ming provinces.

240
00:15:37,820 --> 00:15:39,470
His Majesty just ascended the throne.

241
00:15:39,700 --> 00:15:40,640
His foundation was unstable.

242
00:15:41,140 --> 00:15:43,490
Mr. Yuan sent me to Beijing to join the Night Scout.

243
00:15:44,760 --> 00:15:46,280
I’ve worked hard for five years.

244
00:15:47,670 --> 00:15:49,110
I didn't expect to take over my father's position

245
00:15:49,140 --> 00:15:50,760
and become the Colonel of the Night Scout in Nanjing.

246
00:15:52,540 --> 00:15:53,160
At the same time,

247
00:15:53,890 --> 00:15:55,490
I’ve shown every secret letter of the Night Scout

248
00:15:55,660 --> 00:15:57,040
to Mr. Yuan.

249
00:15:58,330 --> 00:16:00,430
I killed many of my Night Scout comrades.

250
00:16:01,100 --> 00:16:02,050
But I had no choice.

251
00:16:03,230 --> 00:16:05,020
I can only figure out

252
00:16:05,540 --> 00:16:06,620
why my father died

253
00:16:06,640 --> 00:16:07,940
and stay with my sister

254
00:16:07,940 --> 00:16:08,820
by staying with Mr. Yuan.

255
00:16:13,180 --> 00:16:14,460
Mr. Yuan has promised me that

256
00:16:15,740 --> 00:16:17,170
as long as I find the Yuming Lock,

257
00:16:17,990 --> 00:16:19,810
he'll tell me the truth of everything.

258
00:16:29,670 --> 00:16:31,190
I don't care whether you work for Prince Yan

259
00:16:31,220 --> 00:16:32,110
or Yuan Zhongdao.

260
00:16:32,700 --> 00:16:33,780
I don’t care

261
00:16:33,780 --> 00:16:34,960
how many compatriots you have killed.

262
00:16:35,780 --> 00:16:36,740
I only care about you.

263
00:16:42,380 --> 00:16:43,480
We came to Nanjing together.

264
00:16:47,650 --> 00:16:48,760
In the war between the South and the North,

265
00:16:49,740 --> 00:16:50,510
no matter who wins,

266
00:16:51,340 --> 00:16:52,400
I will die.

267
00:16:53,950 --> 00:16:55,440
I just live for an obsession.

268
00:17:05,569 --> 00:17:06,230
Colonel.

269
00:17:08,579 --> 00:17:09,710
I have a presumptuous request.

270
00:17:12,180 --> 00:17:14,300
Please retire from the Colonel of the Night Scout of Nanjing.

271
00:17:15,980 --> 00:17:16,700
Let me do this job.

272
00:17:18,220 --> 00:17:19,310
If you agree,

273
00:17:20,660 --> 00:17:21,930
I will return the favor

274
00:17:23,500 --> 00:17:24,650
and bring you the Yuming Lock.

275
00:17:35,380 --> 00:17:36,910
Uncle Wang, go back to sleep.

276
00:17:37,900 --> 00:17:39,660
Uncle Wang, go home.

277
00:17:39,660 --> 00:17:41,180
It's too late now. Stop drinking.

278
00:17:41,180 --> 00:17:42,480
I'm closing.

279
00:17:52,750 --> 00:17:53,810
I have a big deal.

280
00:17:54,150 --> 00:17:54,990
I promise it'll make money.

281
00:17:58,520 --> 00:17:59,320
Uncle Wang.

282
00:17:59,740 --> 00:18:00,960
I'm leaving. Take care.

283
00:18:01,620 --> 00:18:02,620
