I forgot.

604
00:44:22,570 --> 00:44:24,290
I'm an Imperial Guard who was expelled by you.

605
00:44:24,460 --> 00:44:25,470
There's no Log Book anymore.

606
00:44:26,220 --> 00:44:27,540
Besides, I can't write.

607
00:44:30,090 --> 00:44:31,190
I'll teach you.

608
00:44:37,260 --> 00:44:38,620
Go back to the Investigation Bureau first.

609
00:44:38,660 --> 00:44:39,480
Get the reinstatement.

