00:44:40,530 --> 00:44:41,820
You actually helped me a lot.

611
00:44:43,300 --> 00:44:44,510
Since Xie Kengran is gone.

612
00:44:45,370 --> 00:44:46,610
No one would help me

613
00:44:47,190 --> 00:44:48,650
in the Investigation Bureau.

