00:44:51,500 --> 00:44:52,980
To be frank, being a Brocade-clad Guard is no different from being a farmer,

615
00:44:53,340 --> 00:44:54,030
a trader,

616
00:44:54,380 --> 00:44:55,060
or a theif.

617
00:44:55,060 --> 00:44:55,840
There is no difference.

618
00:44:56,900 --> 00:44:58,090
We all have to live.

619
00:44:59,500 --> 00:45:00,780
It does not matter if you are popular or not.

620
00:45:01,480 --> 00:45:03,860
Have seen so many Brocade-clad Guards in corruption.

621
00:45:04,390 --> 00:45:05,280
I finally realize

622
00:45:06,910 --> 00:45:07,840
